law.text: Every proceeding commenced before June 18, 1970, is deemed to have commenced under this subtitle for the purpose of conducting the proceeding thereafter, except that in the discretion of the commissioner the proceeding may be continued, in whole or in part, as it would have been continued had this subtitle not been enacted.
law.history: Amended 2010 Ky. Acts ch. 24, sec. 1433, effective July 15, 2010. -- Created 1970 Ky. Acts ch. 301, subtit. 33, sec. 10, effective June 18, 1970.
